export default (value: any): value is HTMLElement =>
  value instanceof HTMLElement;

sources.../src/utils/isBoolean.ts: export default (value: unknown): value is boolean => typeof value === 'boolean';
sources.../src/utils/isString.ts: export default (value: unknown): value is string => typeof value === 'string';
sources.../src/utils/isRegex.ts: export default (value: unknown): value is RegExp => value instanceof RegExp;

export default (value: unknown): value is Function =>
  typeof value === 'function';
sources.../src/utils/isWeb.ts:
import { UNDEFINED } from '../constants';

export default typeof window !== UNDEFINED && typeof document !== UNDEFINED;

export default <T>(value: T | T[]): undefined[] | undefined =>
  Array.isArray(value) ? Array(value.length).fill(undefined) : undefined;
